Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.60,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}闇夜之曉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.10,0:24:54.94,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}明天 會到來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍我全身的暗黑魔力  真是令人懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉澤蘿忒·薇露庫麥絲塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望  就由我來實現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來視嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕蟲小技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為魂魄  與所愛之人永遠遊蕩在世間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你得到「碎片」了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯佩爾比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼之主殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至極  事到如今還無法接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉澤蘿忒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要斬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會忘了我是不死之軀吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在「碎片」已經不足  能實現你願望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我這右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼能救結花  救大家和世界的方法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我死就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡故事的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「從那以後兩個人便在一起  過上了幸福的生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡是沒什麼  怎麼了？出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君  去公園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在房間裡讀書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃點東西比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  摔扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去要點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有結花陪你呢  有結花陪你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該感謝結花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你把雷切頂到脖子前的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花用能力將雷切消滅  你才得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉澤蘿忒也失去了戰鬥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然只是暫時性的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞趁機把我們轉移到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是使用能力而疲勞  還有受到刺激了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅  竟然想自盡  你真是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「從那以後兩個人便在一起  過上了幸福的生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為自己明白了  卻是一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能消失  不管發生什麼事都不能離開結花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我的命還在  我要償還結花所給我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨我的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我要打倒莉澤蘿忒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要命還在…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是結花造出來的幻影嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人不是在結花的世界裡的菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿布拉庫薩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寄宿在驅的姐姐身上的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐身上的精靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人菊理自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她認為虛無的碎片只要少一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女莉澤蘿忒的野心就不能實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅的姐姐知道地獄之墜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  所以我的主人才會殺掉劫之眼的主人  她的弟弟驅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而自己也自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？驅可是還活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  驅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿布拉庫薩斯曾經殺了驅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那並不是擁有劫之眼的驅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有劫之眼的驅不是在菊理的世界裡  而是在其他世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花的世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是  所以你才活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花的世界裡的菊理並沒有「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有阿布拉庫薩斯  所以才只有她一個死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全搞不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  兩個不同世界裡的菊理都知曉了同一個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取了一樣的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有「碎片」的那個用精靈阿布拉庫薩斯把驅殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是結花的世界裡的菊理並沒有精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能親手殺掉驅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個驅就是你  你才是劫之眼的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來你應該是和擁有「碎片」的菊理一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知在什麼階段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花用「碎片」的力量把你召喚到了自己的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意之間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰告訴菊理的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是兩個  在除了赤夜之外的六個世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都把事實告訴了菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能特定在哪個世界裡的菊理是「碎片」的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跨越時空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你只把事實告訴菊理？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我接受指令的那時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了菊理之外的「碎片」的主人都太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對姐姐說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「為了拯救世界  你就去死吧」是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是做了下警告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒想到  結局會是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜  驅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都感到非常內疚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是從來都沒有扯上過關係就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是赤夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的主人在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是把結花的力量給封印住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皐月驅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎已經沒有想要自行了斷的意思了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把結花還來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  你就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真老實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你把結花還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅…  君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑月正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  一起墜入地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該相信黑騎士們的轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把我的…  碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她不是人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過除了心以外  都是人造的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以生命為代價的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有這個的話  說不定封印還能夠完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞她擁有穿越時空的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在這能力的基礎上  再加以劫之眼的力量的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能夠將莉澤蘿忒封印在時空的夾縫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得一試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要救驅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要殺他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界的可能性  已經無限接近於零
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  相信一次  也未嘗不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間供我們爭辯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阿瓦利提亞大人現在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法長時間維持封印的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再做無謂的掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能保護你  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  結花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保護別人的  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護好結花的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後  直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深鎖總光之門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惑七星所召
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由自草丘之勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武曲零零
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲之侶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真打  童子切安綱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噬命之刀  童子切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為驅你的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  你也對驅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底還是人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是毀滅  還是守護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸根結底  都是由心做主呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦利提亞大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  就讓一切結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允許結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是起點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望  只不過是為了品嚐絕望而生的  愚蠢的夢境而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自說自話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好不容易才覺察到了自己的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好不容易才決定要從此改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你為什麼又要把明天就此抹去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管誰叫我放手  我都絕不言棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有人說  希望的盡頭  只有絕望在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也決不會相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世事有好亦有壞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世人有善亦有惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是如今不如意  親手改變就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放棄了  不就萬事皆休了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你聽來  也許這只不過是孩子的戲言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻真心實意地這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以為自己是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以為自己是靠著一己之力獨活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  事實卻並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身後  一直都有人在支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有結花在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有結花在我身邊  我才沒有迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是結花的功勞呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我和結花的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都將由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真能守護得住  你就守來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉澤蘿忒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉德？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念  從劫之眼裡頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能奪走這些人的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉德…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前  我看不到世人的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個少年告訴了我這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能明白  莉澤蘿忒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以抹殺這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉德…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不會再猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我苦忍了八百年的孤獨  想要的便只有這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠玉碑的碎片  劫之眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快集氣  美鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童子喲童子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食我血肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身化魔炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪我現世之大怨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無用的抵抗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能讓你得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠地睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴比倫的魔女！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦利提亞大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結…  結花…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了主人的赤夜  已經開始崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有這樣的未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁家就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  驅君你啊  又跟結花來孤男寡女啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行  不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓人家也甜蜜蜜  瘋顛顛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說些神經兮兮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後  我和結花  都沒有再提過赤夜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開那個大不倒翁一看  裡面又出來了一個小不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再打開那小不倒翁一看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有一個更小的不倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又擅自從我錢包裡順手牽羊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  賢久前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話還沒說完呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得用身體來還債  賢久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就150日元嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,150日元還嫌少  你給我站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子和賢久也不知道我們的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡  既沒有菊理姐  也沒有栞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.54,0:24:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.06,0:24:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去阿亞納斯逛逛  要是方便的話  能不能陪我一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.06,0:24:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs17}註：阿亞納斯商場所在的位置正好是赤夜中水晶塔的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.64,0:24:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道這是誰的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.00,0:24:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在這裡  卻有一份安樂與平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.85,0:24:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那不是未來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個世界  便還會擁有明天
